{"tid":1530506,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學生罷課玩法","createTime":"2019-09-02T03:33:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T03:34:51.000Z","uid":2207,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a9b7fee8bc9310066df624212a7bf4b8fc303c96","tid":1530506,"uid":2207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:33:44.000Z","msg":"學生們,<br />\n首先你地要知道, 好多老師都同你地同一陣線。<br />\n<br />\n問題係老師後面, 仲有校長, 家長, 校董會, EDB, 政府, 大陸。<br />\n要成功, 要做到你地想要既效果<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「人數」係唯一關鍵</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n要知道<br />\n學校可以記全班30個學生大過<br />\n不過唔可以記全校1000個學生大過<br />\n黑警可以拉10個學生, 唔可以拉1000個學生<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要有效果, 要安全, 就一定要夠多人。<br />\n<br />\n罷課唔係叫你唔返學<br />\n反而, 你要更加要準時返學<br />\n用你既行為去感染其他同學<br />\n<br />\n加油。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸: 教畜"},{"pid":"eaa5c90ba4c583e69452becdd6e8396f8eaf4f7c","tid":1530506,"uid":2207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:34:50.000Z","msg":"自推 比學生睇"},{"pid":"33feb8b1e7a01d626ba45c0a06ff37d60d7c102a","tid":1530506,"uid":7948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:34:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ALupoHa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FALupoHa.jpg&h=b51370df&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}